author: Cyriacus, Franciscus Niger, fl. 1629
title: Ducatus Mantuae, siue Disquisitio juridica articulis sex comprehensa. ... edita pro serenissimo principe Carolo, duce Mantuae ... Authore Francisco Nigro Cyriaco, ... Accessit Disquisitio alia in eadem causa conscripta à Friderico Bosio, JC. camerae audit
